#
Plotted log2fold values (and the corresponding padj) are the output of the DESeq2 pipeline from a pairwise comparison between an ESC wt and an NPC wt sample.
The standard DEseq2 analysis is run on the data from the Supplemental Table 9, which represents raw reads of the count-normalized cHiC replicates.

- The "loop_annotation" file connects the loop number (i.e., loop22) with its custom annotation (i.e., constant). Custom annotations are provided only for the loops of interest, which are visualised in the Figures and Extended Data Figures.
- res.ESCwt_NPCwt_10kb_bins_21_03_2024.tsv file is the full DEseq2 output file from loop quantification at the Zfp608 TAD.
- "ESCwt_NPCwt_lolipop_input" file is the input file used to make the panelF graph. padj values for this panel come from res.ESCwt_NPCwt_10kb_bins_21_03_2024.tsv file for each loop. 
